channel.title: **First Ever 602 Server And Client**
channel.description:
IMPORTANT: this is a blank server. It is hard to setup if you are just learning to use rsps. If you are looking for a good server to host this is not for you. One day i will release a 602 that is very good but until then i recomend something else
This is a 601 USING 602 cache.
1. Download the cache. http://www.mediafire.com/?ktzyymnkmdw
2 Extract the Cache. Cache goes in C:/ example. [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/2dc8qhv.jpg[/img]
3. Once you have done that, you need to setup xampp, and add the databases for the packets, players and items. http://www.mediafire.com/?diwylojzhjt Cut and paste using dir
4. Download the Server. http://www.mediafire.com/?cntwml54xwz
5. Download the Client. http://www.mediafire.com/?wjnmtwtw1zz
6. Run the Server and Client and enjoy. Use the Account Creation protocol to create an account.
15706, Dungeoneering cape 18348, Dungeoneering experience 18509, Dungeoneering cape (t) 18510, Dungeoneering hood [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/24mudqd.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/140vg9w.jpg[/img]
If you can some how not figure this out here is the link to a tutorial- it breaks down how to do this.
http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,437464.0.html
